  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: dca5f01e15217504780fb2e34a2ce701, type: 3}
  m_Name: Songs
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  songs:
  - type: 0
    lyrics:
    - The pulse of the land beats steady and strong.
    - Infinite stories written in the shifting shadows.
    - Each breath echoes the wisdom of the elders.
    - Clouds gather above the meeting place.
    - Legends wake within the heart of the forest. Stone paths lead us back to the
      beginning.
    - We carry the fire passed through generations. Voices unite in the rhythm of
      the harvest.
    - Tafalong sea is a vision of beauty. Ancient songs drift across the mountain
      range. Roots reach down into the sacred earth.
    - The tongue of the Amis sings deep. We honor the work left by those before.
      Golden sunlight dancing upon the crest.
    - Looking upward to the vast open sky. Our river flows through the ancient valley.
      Walking together on the road of life.
    - Tafalong is the home of our spirit. The face of the Pangcah shines bright.
      We remember the tides of our ancestors.
